      "width": 760,
      "height": 180,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Edge Features Showcase\n\nThis graph demonstrates:\n- **Multi-label edges**: `edge.labels = [start, middle, end]`\n- **Center-segment label placement** (orthogonal)\n- **Multi-edge lane spacing** using `documentSettings.layout.edgeLaneGapPx` (default **10px**)\n\nTry changing **Document Properties → Appearance → Edge lane spacing (px)** to see lanes widen/narrow.",
